cast.overview: A young boy whose parents just divorced finds an unlikely friend and mentor in the misanthropic, bawdy, hedonistic, war veteran who lives next door.
cast.title: St. Vincent

also_known_as: デヴィッド・アイアコノ
details.biography: David Iacono is an American actor and model. On television, he is best known for his role in the Amazon Prime series The Summer I Turned Pretty (2022–2023). He is known for his work on Cinnamon (2023) and Dead Boy Detectives (2024).
details.name: David Iacono
details.place_of_birth: Brooklyn, New York City, New York, USA
